标 → 跑全量 80 条澳大利亚线索\n4. 门槛未达标 → 调整评分阈值\n\n## 历史聊天记录\n\n完整会话记录存放在 `docs/logs/claude-code-sessions/`，详见该目录的 `README.md`。\n\n主要会话:\n- `360b428a` (3.2MB, 1168条) — 项目优化 + 提取脚本迭代 + 工作流规范\n- `db3f6604` (2.5MB, 603条) — KP 管线开发 (Stage 2/3)\n"}}],"usage":{"input_tokens":2212,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":107072,"output_tokens":983,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"},"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_details":null},"type":"assistant","uuid":"92b1115a-d4fb-48a0-93ff-fc92a54d18ee","timestamp":"2026-05-20T01:42:02.328Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"claude-vscode","cwd":"E:\\AI\\TestProject-v2","sessionId":"eb7e8502-d52b-4b66-a1a1-f7790280b67d","version":"2.1.145","gitBranch":"master"}
